data.description: Welcome to the Lake!! Taconic Shores is a private residential community surrounding Robinson Pond, an approximately 120+/- acre lake on the Roeliff Jansen Kill in Copake.This three bedroom, (tax records have as 2-bedrooms) one bath is nestled among the trees and just across the road from the lake. One level, easy living with a wood burning fireplace in living room & will have all of the outdoor space you need for spending time at the lake! The large flat yard, could easily accommodate a garage, and already has a slab there. Renovated in 2023 with new kitchen, flooring, bathroom, full usable basement that doubles size of home. Enjoy year round relaxation or a wonderful weekend getaway at 88 Jefferson Road, on the corner of Lake view.
